Package: parallelRemake
Title: Parallelize Remake-Style Workflows with Makefiles
Version: 0.0.2.9000
Date: 2016-11-19
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = c("William", "Michael"), family = "Landau",  
      email = "will.landau@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph")),
    person(given = c("Richard", "G."), family = "FitzJohn", role = "cph"))
Description: Parallelize a workflow that uses remake (Rich FitzJohn, https://
    richfitz.github.io/) by generating a Makefile, which can distribute the work
    over multiple parallel processes with system("make -j").
License: GPL (>=3)
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
